{"id":498992,"date":[{"year":1969,"month":10,"day":21}],"page":"3","source":"","region":"","masthead":"","special_issue":"","column":"","genre":"","count":"151","ytitle":"","mtitle":"二十年创业炼红心","ftitle":"","authors":["龚咏燕"],"text":[{"type":"paragraph","text":"沪东纺织机械厂　龚咏燕"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"咱们的老工人，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"革命熔炉里的一块纯钢，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"二十年创业炼红心，沿着自力更生的大道向前闯。"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"创家业——走南泥湾的路，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"建厂房——厘钱精神大发扬，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"帮青年——手捧一锅“忆苦饭”，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"当了“官”——机油仍然满身香。"}]}